{"tid":2038880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【孟晚舟案】法院判符合「雙重犯罪」引渡案需繼續審理","createTime":"2020-05-27T18:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T19:22:04.000Z","uid":25334,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c134dc14a08a7f54ac6fb4c5ad26ee5ab2179c05","tid":2038880,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:22:17.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200528&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60986437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200528%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60986437&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=b916f660\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200528%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60986437&h=f2cbcadf\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200528&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60986437</a><br />\n<br />\n華為副董事長孟晚舟是否涉及雙重犯罪，加拿大溫哥華卑詩省最高法院（British Columbia Supreme Court）將於當地時間周三早上11時（即香港時間周四凌晨2時）作出判決。<br />\n<br />\n0200:加拿大法院於當地時間周三宣判，指孟晚舟的控罪屬「雙重犯罪」，意思是被指控的犯罪是在加拿大與美國同時犯罪，故合符引渡到美國的條件，即孟晚舟需要繼續留在加拿大，等候引渡美國的程序。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好消息一個接一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天滅中共 全黨死清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"4642688df0ad560c6d4860b2157aac8b2bc9edb5","tid":2038880,"uid":75448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲係門口yeah得咁開心"},{"pid":"77b8199ce3ebda7ddcac19e32b904b90b79b5b5b","tid":2038880,"uid":61235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T18:23:49.000Z","msg":"人黎，香檳，小鳳姐"},{"pid":"ed3c08100bc11add49abb775fada84b46b861321","tid":2038880,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite